301
00:20:22,510 --> 00:20:24,000
We can defend ourselves from Choeseon, too.

302
00:20:24,000 --> 00:20:28,960
That's why they didn't give you 10th-graders. So, you two can stay safe.

303
00:20:29,810 --> 00:20:32,980
