386
00:27:22,940 --> 00:27:25,640
It'd be hard to beat them.

387
00:27:26,910 --> 00:27:29,460
And the first page of the textbook says...

388
00:27:29,460 --> 00:27:34,210
the goal of studying Korean is to live as a human.

389
00:27:35,480 --> 00:27:40,410
But reading doesn't make me feel more of a human.

390
00:27:42,050 --> 00:27:44,760
I don't know what it means to be a human, either.

391
00:27:47,490 --> 00:27:49,100
Anyway,

392
00:27:50,080 --> 00:27:51,850
I didn't like Korean...

393
