01:00:35,780 --> 01:00:38,460
Looks like you're a Huiwon High student.

780
01:00:38,460 --> 01:00:43,130
Yes. I'd like to consult about the final lecture.

781
01:00:43,130 --> 01:00:44,820
Since it's hard to improve school grades,

782
01:00:44,820 --> 01:00:49,850
some say, "I'll go for the regular admission. I'm expecting this grade."

783
01:00:52,810 --> 01:00:55,900
A Huiwon High student is here for counseling.

784
01:00:58,190 --> 01:00:59,510
Let's go, Ms. Seo.

785
01:00:59,510 --> 01:01:01,890
A student came alone? Not with his mom?

786
01:01:01,890 --> 01:01:03,580
He came alone.

787
01:01:03,580 --> 01:01:05,140
Hurry.

788
01:01:07,680 --> 01:01:09,630
Go see him alone first.

789
01:01:10,910 --> 01:01:13,820
No, you can't do that.

790
01:01:13,820 --> 01:01:15,740
He's your first student.

791
01:01:15,740 --> 01:01:20,260
Don't think, "I have to lure him and start a class."

792
01:01:20,260 --> 01:01:24,340
Just enjoy everything the first student can give you.

793
01:01:25,030 --> 01:01:26,330
Okay.

794
01:01:27,010 --> 01:01:28,740
I'll be right back.

795
01:01:36,610 --> 01:01:38,760
- Nice to see you, Si Wu. 
- Hello.

796
01:01:38,760 --> 01:01:40,360
Hi.

797
01:01:44,810 --> 01:01:47,900
I knew you'd come, but I wondered when.

798
01:01:47,900 --> 01:01:50,520
Thank you for not making me wait too long.

799
01:01:51,530 --> 01:01:53,780
Do you have somewhere to be afterward?

800
01:01:53,780 --> 01:01:56,180
No, I don't have a class today.

801
01:01:56,180 --> 01:01:57,660
That's great.

802
01:02:01,310 --> 01:02:02,800
Why do you ask?

803
01:02:03,410 --> 01:02:07,630
I didn't get to have a good look at you last time.

804
01:02:07,630 --> 01:02:09,710
As you know,

805
01:02:09,710 --> 01:02:13,230
I was humiliated by the whole universe that day.

806
01:02:14,850 --> 01:02:18,930
So, I'm finally taking it all in now.

807
01:02:20,630 --> 01:02:24,150
I haven't paid for the class yet.

808
01:02:24,150 --> 01:02:25,620
You...

809
01:02:26,810 --> 01:02:30,390
You're cutthroat, aren't you?

810
01:02:30,390 --> 01:02:35,620
Okay. Let's take the normal steps for a smooth admission.

811
01:02:35,620 --> 01:02:38,900
Just answer the question I ask freely.

812
01:02:38,900 --> 01:02:43,820
I prepared answers to the questions you might ask.

813
01:02:43,820 --> 01:02:46,600
Sounds good. Can we hear it?

814
01:02:46,600 --> 01:02:47,970
Yes.

815
01:02:48,870 --> 01:02:51,080
I'm in 10th grade at Huiwon High.

816
01:02:51,080 --> 01:02:55,130
I don't usually like Korean, but I'm not bad at it.

817
01:02:55,130 --> 01:02:59,030
I got the perfect score in the midterm.

818
01:03:00,250 --> 01:03:04,420
I consistently study Korean for an hour or two per day.

819
01:03:04,420 --> 01:03:06,940
I don't study on my own when there's an academy class.

820
01:03:07,670 --> 01:03:12,440
I don't procrastinate or skim over homework.

821
01:03:12,440 --> 01:03:13,930
And...

822
01:03:16,130 --> 01:03:20,570
it's hard for me to understand and analyze literature.

823
01:03:20,570 --> 01:03:23,610
I can blindly memorize and get the perfect score,

824
01:03:24,330 --> 01:03:28,600
but I get very flustered when I encounter unfamiliar text.

825
01:03:32,150 --> 01:03:35,490
I've said my goal is to go to medical school in Seoul,

826
01:03:35,490 --> 01:03:37,720
but that's more my mom's goal.

827
01:03:37,720 --> 01:03:39,780
I'm not so sure yet.

828
01:03:42,270 --> 01:03:45,340
I haven't decided on the elective subject yet.

829
01:03:45,340 --> 01:03:48,740
My question is whether the academy offers scholarships.

830
01:03:53,810 --> 01:03:56,350
Yes. That's it.

831
01:04:00,440 --> 01:04:02,280
Do you dislike Korean?

832
01:04:05,430 --> 01:04:07,340
I think so.

833
01:04:08,340 --> 01:04:09,900
How strange.

834
01:04:09,900 --> 01:04:12,430
Aren't you a good writer, by chance?

835
01:04:13,060 --> 01:04:15,140
I'm not talking about essay answers.

836
01:04:15,140 --> 01:04:17,930
Isn't there a kind of writing you're good at?

837
01:04:17,930 --> 01:04:20,790
Criticism or blog writing?

838
01:04:21,970 --> 01:04:23,940
How did you know?

839
01:04:25,490 --> 01:04:30,060
Because you're an excellent teenager who has to be a good writer.

840
01:04:36,680 --> 01:04:38,990
I haven't paid for the class yet.

841
01:04:38,990 --> 01:04:41,110
Let's talk about the scholarship first.

842
01:04:41,110 --> 01:04:43,940
I'm very confident in that matter.

843
01:04:43,940 --> 01:04:47,280
I was the first scholarship student at this academy.

844
01:04:47,280 --> 01:04:49,460
It's a glorious title.

845
01:04:52,080 --> 01:04:54,400
Yes, Director. You can start eating.

846
01:04:54,400 --> 01:04:58,040
I'm having a major issue at the academy.

847
01:04:58,040 --> 01:05:02,210
Yes, I'll let you know when I get there. Okay.

848
01:05:08,860 --> 01:05:12,470
Will we be able to start a class?

849
01:05:12,470 --> 01:05:15,960
Not sure. It's just that one student.

850
01:05:15,960 --> 01:05:18,990
We don't know how influential he is at school.

851
01:05:18,990 --> 01:05:22,010
Academically or socially.

852
01:05:22,640 --> 01:05:24,580
I should've asked

853
01:05:24,580 --> 01:05:28,530
who the only student was, and what he was like.

854
01:05:28,530 --> 01:05:34,380
If we get to start a class, won't it be a major event?

855
01:05:39,870 --> 01:05:44,420
We didn't make a serious mistake, did we?

856
01:05:44,420 --> 01:05:47,960
The elision will reduce the number of syllables.

857
01:05:47,960 --> 01:05:50,970
Keep that in mind and try question No. 3 again.

858
01:05:50,970 --> 01:05:52,970
What's incorrect?

859
01:06:10,010 --> 01:06:12,800
- I heard a Huiwon High student came. 
 - Yes.

860
01:06:12,800 --> 01:06:14,960
That's a major event.

861
01:06:14,960 --> 01:06:17,320
We don't know yet.

862
01:06:17,320 --> 01:06:20,480
He alone can't start a class.

863
01:06:50,010 --> 01:06:52,070
The next text.

864
01:06:53,360 --> 01:06:55,310
Let's take a 15-minute break.

865
01:07:24,900 --> 01:07:26,540
Get home safely.

866
01:07:28,300 --> 01:07:31,900
- Take care. 
 - Bye.

867
01:07:31,900 --> 01:07:33,920
Did he sign up?

868
01:07:33,920 --> 01:07:35,650
It's over.

869
01:07:51,610 --> 01:07:53,540
As for the other students...

870
01:07:59,180 --> 01:08:02,430
They get off school early tomorrow, so...

871
01:08:05,240 --> 01:08:07,340
they'll be coming then.

872
01:08:08,520 --> 01:08:12,210
So, how many do you think will come? Will it be enough to start a class?

873
01:08:12,210 --> 01:08:13,540
Yes, that won't be an issue.

874
01:08:13,540 --> 01:08:16,620
Gosh, seriously?

875
01:08:16,620 --> 01:08:20,540
We need to prepare a nice classroom. Right, Assistant Director?

876
01:08:20,540 --> 01:08:22,570
Gosh, congratulations.

877
01:08:22,570 --> 01:08:23,880
Thank you.

878
01:08:23,880 --> 01:08:26,390
Congrats, Team Leader Seo.

879
01:08:26,390 --> 01:08:29,070
- Ms. Seo.
 - Let's talk after the class.

880
01:08:29,070 --> 01:08:31,150
I'm in the middle of my class.

881
01:08:31,150 --> 01:08:33,340
Let's talk in my office.

882
01:08:33,340 --> 01:08:34,780
- Okay.
 - Let's go.

883
01:08:34,780 --> 01:08:36,180
Let's go.

