01:09:18,140 --> 01:09:22,150
 The Midnight Romance in Hagwon 

886
01:09:22,150 --> 01:09:24,450
 You can join Choeseon Korean. 

887
01:09:24,450 --> 01:09:27,420
 How disappointing. I was hoping for a beautiful goodbye. 

888
01:09:27,420 --> 01:09:29,180
 Don't act all high and mighty. 

889
01:09:29,180 --> 01:09:30,380
 Geez! 

890
01:09:30,380 --> 01:09:33,300
 I can't imagine the academy without Seo Hye Jin. 

891
01:09:33,300 --> 01:09:38,080
 Someone like that can get scary once they change their mind. 

892
01:09:38,080 --> 01:09:39,780
 Do you have time to loaf around? 

893
01:09:39,780 --> 01:09:41,280
 Just focus on your goal. 

894
01:09:41,280 --> 01:09:44,620
 I'm trying way harder to hold back than you think. 

895
01:09:44,620 --> 01:09:47,720
 Ms. Seo, you're such a headache. 

896
01:09:47,720 --> 01:09:49,650
 What am I supposed to do when you do this? 

